Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.80,0:00:47.70,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}每日从早到晚 你都在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.82,0:00:52.26,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}这样的生活不断重复
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.73,0:00:55.35,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}一觉醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.50,0:00:57.86,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你已泡好热咖啡等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:01:02.44,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}紧紧抱住你的左臂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.63,0:01:07.53,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}以前曾屈指等待你的出现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.60,0:01:12.62,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}如今见到你的时间是越来越多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.77,0:01:16.93,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,150)\be1}这样的幸福谁曾料到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.95,0:01:22.54,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,200)\be1}你和我 都堕入了爱河
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.65,0:01:27.46,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.60,0:01:30.84,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}初次体会到的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.18,0:01:34.99,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Oh 我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.10,0:01:37.72,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}永远永远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:42.58,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}此情不变
