Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.23,0:23:19.33,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}就禁不住想去触摸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.46,0:23:22.64,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你那湿润的双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.29,0:23:26.98,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}和你嬉戏时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.20,0:23:34.83,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}只以为彼此关系不错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.30,0:23:42.03,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}恋爱的开端
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.29,0:23:48.21,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}就像预报出错的天气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.37,0:23:53.96,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}对着雨后的彩虹伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:24:00.26,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在你身边 我就能变得坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.38,0:24:06.17,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}终于察觉到 想你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.26,0:24:11.75,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}心情是如此的激动
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.83,0:24:14.74,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}昨晚梦里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.88,0:24:17.34,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}又见你的身影
