Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.10,0:00:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 大海的对面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看到一座大山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的哦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------AVAN-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.33,0:01:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:01:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美也 梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:01:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你心神不定的样子 很可疑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.55,0:02:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我现在跟美也一起去买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.38,0:02:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一也一起来么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 去买什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在商场搞圣诞大酬宾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.93,0:02:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看有没啥便宜货啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.88,0:02:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 先逛逛再说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就不跟森岛学姐一起回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行 我也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.92,0:02:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.13,0:02:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梨穗 这样就弄到个苦力啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯～哎？ 不能全让纯一来拿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要适可而止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 趁老哥还没改变主意快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美也 不用这么急吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买买～买买～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.71,0:02:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,470)\fad(0,500)}买东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.17,0:02:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,470)}完全进入圣诞状态了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 圣诞快到了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉～老哥今年也得过个寂寞圣诞节啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今…今年我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小梨穗 快看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.04,0:03:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢巧克力蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.43,0:03:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞节快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得快点约她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年要跟森岛学姐过个快乐的圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森岛学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？啊什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 老哥是想去厕所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 早说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 你快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.64,0:03:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 憋着对身体不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.49,0:03:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮的小姐 请救我出去熊～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.35,0:03:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橘？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:03:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓到你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 吓死我了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTA-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,WOW 成功 获得小熊熊～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 多亏你吓我一下 碰巧就抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.22,0:04:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森岛学姐 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在有时间么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有 闲得很
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们在这里玩一阵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我很少去游戏中心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有什么能两人一起玩的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.93,0:04:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里输入名字的缩写
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是啥 算好还是坏？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐竟会因为与我适合度不高而不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在她心里这么有地位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算再来一次 结果也一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那请学姐再输入一次名字缩写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐不是HM么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个就行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,L是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好高
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞掂 超成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下神清气爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 L是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐姓森岛 应该是M才对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,L是Lovely的L
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没跟橘提起过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原名是森岛·Lovely·遥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lovely是中间名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥 学姐还是混血儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 呃 我外公是英国人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外婆是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我算是四分之一混血
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此…有这回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这回事个头啊 圣诞的事得快点约她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 爽过以后就回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.81,0:06:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次能不能陪一下我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真少见呢 你会这样来约我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐 不冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我每天都来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就看不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我以前在这里见过你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1年前那时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好也是傍晚这个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 大海的对面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看到一座大山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来那里有座山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气好时 能清楚看到大海对面的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都没发现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟谁很像么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是 很像我家以前养的小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是你那为难的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.07,0:07:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时我很消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 多亏学姐跟我搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉轻松了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过后没多久 发现原来你是我们学校的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是吓了一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下 原来橘就是「公园君」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥 公园君？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我对那天印象很深
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后跟人说起遇到了个很有趣的人时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不知道叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就随便起了个「公园君」的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我就是公园君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天来公园是有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我3岁时开始养的一条叫约翰的小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:07:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一年前的圣诞死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后每次想起它都很伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过当时想 这样下去约翰在天上肯定会担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心不下我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就来了约翰最喜欢来的这个公园
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提醒自己打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后有个男生就坐在约翰最喜欢的这张长凳上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男生就是我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你坐着那感觉 跟约翰沮丧的时候一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是觉得不能放着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 一定是约翰安排我跟橘相遇的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来 为什么当时橘会这么沮丧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两年前 我曾在这公园等人约会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 是等女孩子么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橘很有一套啊 真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 被对方放了鸽子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来整整一年都耿耿于怀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时在这公园回想起那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就很沮丧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时学姐跟我搭话 救赎了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能再救我一次吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,24日平安夜 请跟我约会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不愿意跟我约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每年圣诞 外公外婆都从英国过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全家一起开派对 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来…是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 若是邀你参加我家的派对 你来么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没问题的话 平安夜一起过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！乐意之至
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 彻底迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪美也说些奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.65,0:10:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.34,0:10:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种日子让女生等 不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 橘 你头上都冒烟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路跑过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑到头上冒烟 我都不好意思生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们接下来去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.25,0:11:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是学姐家么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是酒店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来酒店干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你一路跑过来我是很开心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.83,0:11:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但总不能向家人介绍个浑身汗臭的男朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以先来这里洗掉汗气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.10,0:11:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然叫这么大声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.23,0:11:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是初次约会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就来酒店 这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问 学姐你觉得可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好酒店有泳衣出租
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会在酒店的泳池洗掉汗气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 泳池啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.38,0:11:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又能瞻仰森岛学姐的泳衣打扮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是新买的泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:11:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…一点都不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当合适 很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 既然如此你应该快点赞我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我看入迷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 让你神魂颠倒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 我们游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞节却来泳池游泳 意外地有意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确很有意思 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不习惯 有点突兀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是跟学姐一起过圣诞就很棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然还在泳池一起游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢承认这是现实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都我跟在一起了 不准看其他女生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,误会啊 我没看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说 眼前有学姐 没必要看其他女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是吗 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…是
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------------以下取自萌月字幕组出品BDRip字幕----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 橘君出了好多汗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是...是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身上明显汗多好多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这...这是...正在和学姐的肌肤亲密接触而且...\N（遥：看来橘君刚才一定很努力的游泳了啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和学姐的汗...混杂在一起了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.52,0:13:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样一同滴落...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.69,0:13:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我会以不服输的精神努力流汗的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------------以上取自萌月字幕组出品BDRip字幕----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 全身清爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来终于要见学姐家人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.86,0:14:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 换衣服费时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…跟你家人碰头的时间 没问题么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我都给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.74,0:14:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以忘记啊 学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来 约好几点碰头来着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 约好是1小时前碰头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 那是在哪集合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约好在这酒店的上层见面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.05,0:14:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不用这么着急
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.39,0:14:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.41,0:14:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不…已经迟到了一小时 得抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 真强硬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:15:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 越来越往上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我畏高…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太害怕了 得找个话题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学…学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要见哪几位家人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 其实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为飞机的关系 外公他们来不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就我们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥 就我们俩？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…你父母呢 他们怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说外公他们来不了就没意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以留在家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.52,0:15:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 在家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是呢 难得预约到的房间不能浪费啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就来过夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确浪费是不好的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾 还想多看一会夜景呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:15:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打搅了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看你看 还能看得见夜景哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道厕所怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 厕所也很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,WOW 浴池也很大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得来了 我先去洗个澡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.03,0:16:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 洗澡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很少有机会能泡这么大个浴池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不泡就浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准偷窥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不偷窥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,WOW 回答得好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先去洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还真去洗了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我是不是也应该一起去洗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 我跟学姐还不是那种关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:16:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过真想到这种关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到真的能跟森岛学姐一起过平安夜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久之前想都不敢想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.31,0:17:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前被甩的时候真的好难过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 还好没有气馁再攻略了一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才能一起过平安夜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you～还好赶在游泳部的杂烩卖光前买到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.67,0:17:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告一段落了呢 塚原学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 七咲 你也可以走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你弟弟不是在等么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的…不过还没收拾完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟其他部员会收拾的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 谢谢学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子也有在加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白色圣诞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.39,0:18:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来 接下来该怎么过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐洗完出来 我也去洗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确 不洗的话挺不妙的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙在什么地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.11,0:18:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不跟刚才一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 停电吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为难为情 我关了灯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这身打扮是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不来偷窥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不偷窥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.72,0:18:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 原来偷窥才是必选项吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不喜欢我么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢的话 不会忍不住去偷窥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这可不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.78,0:19:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不再一次向我表白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.31,0:19:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前明明说过会跟我表白的啊 不管多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.09,0:19:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…一直在等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直一直都在等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为你讨厌我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为你放弃我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好寂寞 好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.74,0:19:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前从没试过这么喜欢一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次有了不想让给任何人的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…都不知道自己该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 要是我能做得更好就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连好好表白都做不到的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐还会要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.89,0:20:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你的表白很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二次表白 头一回让我有了心跳的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我才是不知如何好好传达自己的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我不知道怎么去好好表白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕你会厌烦我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直担心 不安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐只要保持这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所喜欢的森岛学姐 就是这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我会好好表白的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 请你不要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.54,0:21:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫遥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要一直叫学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫 我就不哭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想永远跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜欢你 最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经过了10年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.73,0:21:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们处得还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啦 响
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.21,0:21:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们超恩爱的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.32,0:21:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是 两个怪人凑一块儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.39,0:22:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定能过得好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.11,0:22:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的通缉犯 现在要逮捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.77,0:22:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,响 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.99,0:22:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 橘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.97,0:22:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们每天都这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.15,0:22:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是偶尔啦 相当相当偶尔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.29,0:22:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了呢 塚原学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.07,0:22:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当医生果然很忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.62,0:22:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来 你这样也能当刑警
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.11,0:22:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本的治安有没有问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.64,0:22:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,响 纯一可能守护不了日本的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.91,0:22:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他说好了会一辈子都保护我的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.74,0:22:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遥～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.77,0:22:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你 就如爱天上的繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.85,0:22:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,435)\fs23\fsp-1}（是是 我看到都饱了）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.85,0:22:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也爱你 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.58,0:22:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遥～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.31,0:22:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一～
Comment: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------NEXT-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.86,0:24:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集预告
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.11,0:24:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 下集开始就是棚町薰篇了哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.85,0:24:30.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰 别太乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.79,0:24:33.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢 看我一开始就抽飞你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.57,0:24:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 请你掌握好度
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.29,0:24:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 欢乐地上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.82,0:24:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.64,0:24:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的真讨厌 明明这么开心的～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.96,0:24:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别用手肘撞我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.09,0:24:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 我不是什么「亲爱的」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.07,0:24:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一集 损友
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.07,0:24:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初中就开始打交道的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.58,0:24:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟薰的新故事 即将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.21,0:24:52.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬请期待
